metadata.name: Gaia The Birth Of An End
metadata.description:
The Wonderland series after was completed, immediately winning 2 International awards.

The Buyer of this NFT will be able to claim The Wonderland Book (Collector’s edition box set in value of $8.000) Book signed and numbered, and accompanied with a certificate of authenticity. 
The book will come presented in a beautiful hand-crafted fabric-covered clamshell box. 

The box is deep-set, and measures 57x47x13cm, weighing 10 kg.  The highlight of this set is the exquisite solid bronze sculpture of The White Queen’s key, forged by London Bronze Casting and specially patinated by the bronze artist Derek Bayley. 

Portfolio Slip Case+ 3 Limited Edition Prints - Matching fabric-covered portfolio slipcase (fitted to the size of box). Contains 3 signed Limited Edition prints of The White Queen Trilogy (The Queen’s Armada, The White Queen, The Faraway Tree). Prints are fitted to the size of the box -Paper size 50 cm ( equivalent to a 20 x 16 inch print).
